This paper involves the use of machine learning for image analysis and prediction of molecular properties, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also involves the use of computational methods for analyzing complex molecular profiling data, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
